OOC: Oops... I knew I forgot a plot somewhere...

::Cygnar::
       He finally arrives at Galvatron's base.  He unlocks it and walks 
inside to begin his quest to revive Galvatron.  He gradually makes his way to 
the command chair and surveys his new charge.  Yes, I could get used to this.
